Welcome to the races!

Newcomers of N1 have more than just a Welcome Package up their sleeve to set a good jump-start! The welcome tournament is extremely convenient for the new racers and available only for them. Score with multipliers instead of bets, and play on both real and bonus money! Good to go!

If you have less than four deposits, join the week-long tournament every Monday! Play your favorite slots and try to get the biggest multiplier to become one of the 60 winners to share the 500 CP + 500 EUR + 500 FS prize pool!

Jump-start!

Rules

  1. 🙋 Qualifying: the event is available for players with less than four deposits;
  2. 💰 Bet with real or bonus money;
  3. ⏱️ Time of the event: every week, from Monday 9:00 UTC to the next Monday 8:59 UTC;
  4. 🎰 Qualifying games: all slot games;
  5. ✔️ Minimum bet: not limited;
  6. 🔝 Win condition. Strategy: points. Players earn victory points for each multiplier they get (win:bet ratio). The bigger the multiplier is, the bigger the number of points is:
    • 3-4: 5 points;
    • 5-14: 25 points;
    • 15-29: 50 points;
    • 30-49: 150 points;
    • 50-99: 300 points;
    • 100: 500 points;
    • 101+: 999 points.
  7. Players get extra points for all qualifying bets made. Any bet, winning or losing, equals 1 point. The total score in progress is displayed on the leaderboard. The points are summed up. At the end of the tournament, the top 60 players with the highest scores win.
  8. 🏆 Prize pool: 500 CP + 500 EUR + 500 FS to the Rise of Merlin slot (Play'n GO!).
  9. If the slot for the FS prize is not available in the player’s region, standard FS will be credited to the alternative slot: Gemmed! (BSG).
  10. 💳 The money prizes have a wagering requirement of x5. The FS prizes have a wagering requirement of x15.
